Package com.kallasoft.smugmug.api.json.v1_2_0.images

Class Summary
ChangePosition This method changes the position of an image within it's album.
ChangeSettings This method updates specific settings for a given image specified by ImageID.
Delete This method deletes the specified image.
Get This method will fetch all the ImageIDs for the album specified by AlbumID.
GetEXIF This method will return camera and photograph details about the image specified by ImageID.
GetInfo This method will return details about the image specified by ImageID.
GetStats Gets transfer statistic for the given Image during the given Month.
GetURLs This method will return all the URLs for the various sizes of the image specified by ImageID.
Upload This method will upload a file to the specified Album (identified by AlbumID) with the required parameters.
UploadFromURL This method will upload a file from a specified URL to the specified Album (identified by AlbumID) with the required parameters.
UploadHTTPPut This method will upload a file to the specified album (identified by X-Smug-AlbumID) or replace an existing image (identified by X-Smug-ImageID) with the required parameters identified by the values of UploadHTTPPut.HTTP_HEADERS.
